	      <witDetail wit="#C">ante correctionem</witDetail>-->
	  <rdg wit="#A">somasūrya</rdg>
	</app>vibhedena vinayas tatra kāraṇam</l>
      </lg>

      <note target="#_10.85" resp="#sr" xml:id="pasam_10.85">
	<p><mentioned>bhuvane</mentioned> jagati.
	<mentioned>siddheti</mentioned> purāṇādyāgamena niścayam āpitā.
	<mentioned>sūrya</mentioned><app>
	<lem wit="#D"><mentioned>soma</mentioned></lem>
	<rdg wit="#C">sauma</rdg>
	</app><mentioned>vibhedene</mentioned>ti sūryavaṃśyāḥ kecit somavaṃśyāś ca kecid iti
	<mentioned>vinaya</mentioned> eva <mentioned>tatra kāraṇam</mentioned> …
	</p>
